metadata.description:
00 - [ ZERO ゼロ ] / _Legacies
[ ze Luna ゼルナ ]

1st piece of the _Legacies collection of the [ze Luna] universe minted on Foundation. 

Focused on neo-mecha themes & inspired by Japanese-Korean sensibilities, _Legacies is geared towards a more detailed & refined art form aimed at portraying the many avatars of the world of [ze Luna].

2000 x 2500 pixels
300 DPI
